Description.BulletDescription:
Equipped with AMD Ryzen 3 7320C, 2.4GHz (Up to Turbo Boost 4.1 GHz, 4 cores, 8 threads).
The 14-inch WUXGA display provides clear and sharp visuals, making it suitable for work and multimedia consumption. 1920 x 1200 resolution brings clear visuals. 
8GB RAM is designed for basic tasks, the high-bandwith DDR5 RAM run your applications smoothly, as well as multiple programs. Up to 2TB storage capacity is suitable for saving all your files and provides enough space to save more data.
Stay connected with Wi-Fi 6 and Bluetooth built in, 1x USB 3.2 Gen 2 Type-A, 2x USB 3.2 Gen 2 Type-C, HDMI 2.1, Micro SD card reader, 1x Headphone/Speaker/Line-Out Jack, enabling you to stay connected and access the internet wirelessly.
Running on Chrome OS, this laptop offers a streamlined and secure computing experience. You can access a wide range of apps from the Chrome Web Store.
